<L>__{exterior mountain, flat rocky area night}
<A>__{a clap of thunder. lightning flashes reveal rain pouring down on the house. beneath it, carl and russell are kept dry, sitting around a pathetic flickering campfire. carl looks at dug, asleep, wrapped around the bird's leg. he rolls his eyes and looks up at the house.}
<C>__{carl}
<D>__{well, thanks for keeping us dry anyway, ellie.}
<C>__{russell }
<D>__{which one's the front?}
