<C>__{russell}
<D>__{there!}
<A>__{russell struggles with a tent pole, trying to winch it into place. carl can't watch. an off screen smack! russell walks to carl. miraculously, he looks unscathed.}
<C>__{russell}
<D>__{all done.}
<A>__{russell turns, revealing a large red welt on his face.}
<C>__{russell}
<P>__{(pointing to tent)}
<D>__{that's for you!}
